<div class="fp three-block">
	<h6><strong>COLUMBIA THEOLOGICAL SEMINARY</strong> EXISTS TO EDUCATE AND NURTURE FAITHFUL, IMAGINATIVE, AND EFFECTIVE LEADERS FOR THE SAKE OF THE CHURCH AND THE WORLD.</h6>
	<div class="three-blocks">
				        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 tb_block" data-tab="EncounteringGod">
		        	<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus tb_plus"></span>
		        	<h2>Encountering God</h2>
		        </div>
		        		        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 tb_block" data-tab="CultivatingLeaders">
		        	<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus tb_plus"></span>
		        	<h2>Cultivating Leaders</h2>
		        </div>
		        		        <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4 tb_block" data-tab="TransformingCommunities">
		        	<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-plus tb_plus"></span>
		        	<h2>Transforming Communities</h2>
		        </div>
		        	</div>
	<div class="three-blocks-overlay">
		<ul class="nav nav-tabs col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1" role="tablist">
						        <li class="col-md-4 col-xs-12 EncounteringGod" role="presentation"><a href="#EncounteringGod" aria-controls="EncounteringGod" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Encountering God</a></li>
			   			        <li class="col-md-4 col-xs-12 CultivatingLeaders" role="presentation"><a href="#CultivatingLeaders" aria-controls="CultivatingLeaders" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Cultivating Leaders</a></li>
			   			        <li class="col-md-4 col-xs-12 TransformingCommunities" role="presentation"><a href="#TransformingCommunities" aria-controls="TransformingCommunities" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Transforming Communities</a></li>
			   		 </ul>
		<div class="clearfix"></div>
		<div class="tab-content">
						        <div role="tabpanel" class="fade tab-pane col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1" id="EncounteringGod"><p>God is living and active in the world near and far. In academically rigorous classes, we study the work God is already doing, challenging students to imagine what God will do through them and their peers. As an educational institution of the Presbyterian Church (USA), Columbia Seminary is a community of theological inquiry and formation for ministry in the service of the Church of Jesus Christ. </p></div>
			   			        <div role="tabpanel" class="fade tab-pane col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1" id="CultivatingLeaders"><p>We are preparing visionary leaders who bring clarity and direction to their ministries, leaders who dwell in the realm of possibility, choosing to enact what can be instead of settling for what is. Internships are one of the many avenues for students to learn and practice their leadership.</p></div>
			   			        <div role="tabpanel" class="fade tab-pane col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1" id="TransformingCommunities"><p>We shape and partner with communities in new, profound, and prophetic ways. We boldly proclaim the Gospel and actively seek God's justice in the church and the world. Campus life includes regular worship, fellowship opportunities, and community meals. Beyond the campus, students unite their education with society's most pressing issues.</p></div>
			   		</div>
